#*: That the spent earth may gather '''heart''' again.
# {{label|en|archaic}} {{non-gloss definition|A term of affectionate or kindly and familiar address.}}
#* ''Listen, dear '''heart''', we must go now.''
#* {{rfdate|and other bibliographic particulars}} {{w|Shakespeare}}
#*: I speak to thee, my '''heart'''.
